translates to "Gateway".

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:54.500 align:middle line:84%
On the Western point
of Gujarat in India

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:57.320 align:middle line:84%
sits the modern
day city of Dwarka.

00:00:57.320 --> 00:01:01.280 align:middle line:84%
This site is one of the seven
legendary sacred pilgrimage

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:03.620 align:middle line:90%
sites from the Hindu traditions.

00:01:03.620 --> 00:01:08.390 align:middle line:84%
