massive city, 5 miles long,

00:03:18.310 --> 00:03:21.490 align:middle line:84%
2 miles wide, possibly
two separate cities.

00:03:21.490 --> 00:03:23.770 align:middle line:84%
And when they
began dating debris

00:03:23.770 --> 00:03:25.630 align:middle line:84%
found from within
the cities, the dates

00:03:25.630 --> 00:03:30.650 align:middle line:84%
