9,500 years before present,

00:03:30.650 --> 00:03:33.130 align:middle line:84%
and maybe a little
bit older than that.

00:03:33.130 --> 00:03:37.840 align:middle line:84%
Placing them precisely at the
time of the Younger Dryas,

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:41.230 align:middle line:84%
and the results of
the Younger Dryas.

00:03:41.230 --> 00:03:44.320 align:middle line:84%
