during the Younger Dryas

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:53.650 align:middle line:90%
then it was after the flood.

00:03:53.650 --> 00:03:56.740 align:middle line:10%
So what we're looking
at is the remains

00:03:56.740 --> 00:04:00.340 align:middle line:10%
of a city that was right on
the edge of the shore that

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:05.320 align:middle line:10%
