comet or a combination of all

00:04:10.940 --> 00:04:11.740 align:middle line:10%
of those.

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:14.890 align:middle line:84%
We know factually that
the sea level did rise

00:04:14.890 --> 00:04:18.820 align:middle line:84%
