because the date does not

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:26.500 align:middle line:84%
fit in to the history
as that history is

00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:28.280 align:middle line:90%
written into the books today.

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:30.700 align:middle line:84%
The question is,
once again, will we

00:04:30.700 --> 00:04:34.330 align:middle line:84%
